= Plugin: InsertNote  =

Allows for the insertion of footnotes/endnotes. Supports:

  * Automatic numbering
  * Automatic linking to anchors
  * Links back to each specific citation
  * Saves previously referenced notes for easy reuse
  * Cleanup of unreferenced notes (or references to non-existent notes)

[wiki:Plugins Back to Plugins]

== Configuration ==

**See the [wiki:NewbieGuide#ProvideSomeConfiguration NewbieGuide] for how to set configuration values in general, the below configuration options are available for this plugin.**

There is no configuration required for this plugin at present.